snippet.title: Dr Doyle and The Mystery of the Cloche Hat - Trailer
snippet.description:
A point & click mystery adventure game.

Armed with his straps, his wits and an inquisitive nature that knows no bounds Dr. Doyle sets out to find the truth and solve the mystery of the cloche hat.

Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=680800526
